com.amplifyframework.predictions.aws

Class AWSPredictionsEscapeHatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.predictions.aws.AWSPredictionsEscapeHatch

  • public final class AWSPredictionsEscapeHatch
extends java.lang.Object
    An escape hatch for Predictions, which gives direct access to the AWS service APIs. Use this to perform low-level operations that are not exposed by Amplify, directly.
